title: RTB - Geography #3 - Referrers by City & Region

dashboard_elements.note_text:
Purpose: View page views results by Referrer Medium and broken down by City and Region.
Use the Referrer Medium filter to focus on a specific referrer as needed and use the City and Region filter to focus on a specific city as needed.

More Information: To learn more about web analytics definitions for metrics and how to navigate standard dashboards, go to the Web Analytics Guide.
dashboard_elements.title: Referrers by City & Region

field.label: Page Views Page View Start Date
field.name: page_views.page_view_start_date

field.label: Page Views Referrer Medium
field.name: page_views.referrer_medium
field.sql:
CASE
          WHEN ${TABLE}.refr_medium IS NULL THEN 'direct'
          WHEN ${TABLE}.refr_medium = 'unknown' THEN 'other'
          ELSE  ${TABLE}.refr_medium END

field.label: Page Views Geo City and Region
field.name: page_views.geo_city_and_region
field.sql:
CASE
       WHEN (${TABLE}.geo_city = '' OR ${TABLE}.geo_city IS NULL) THEN ${TABLE}.geo_country_name
       WHEN (${TABLE}.geo_country = 'CA' OR ${TABLE}.geo_country = 'US') THEN ${TABLE}.geo_city || ' - ' || ${TABLE}.geo_region_name
       ELSE ${TABLE}.geo_city || ' - ' || ${TABLE}.geo_country_name
      END
